---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Safeguarding & Privacy" description="Child protection policy and privacy policy for Greencrest Advent School">
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-dark to-green-darker text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Safeguarding & Privacy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-green-light">Protecting Our Students and Your Information</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Child Protection Policy -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="heading-primary mb-8">Child Protection Policy</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          At Greencrest Advent School, the safety and well-being of every child is our highest priority. We are committed to creating a safe, secure, and nurturing environment where children can learn and grow without fear.
        </p>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Our Commitment</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-dark mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>All staff members undergo thorough background checks and child protection training</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-dark mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Clear policies and procedures for reporting and handling concerns</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-dark mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Safe recruitment practices for all staff and volunteers</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-dark mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Regular training on child protection for all staff members</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-dark mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Designated Child Protection Officer on staff</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="text-green-dark mr-2">✓</span>
            <span>Secure campus with appropriate access controls</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Reporting Concerns</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          If you have any concerns about a child's safety or well-being, please contact our Child Protection Officer immediately:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-green-light/20 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Child Protection Officer:</strong><br>
            Email: safeguarding@greencrestadvent.ac.ke<br>
            Phone: +254 727 568 790<br>
            Available: Monday - Friday, 8:00 AM - 5:00 PM
          </p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          All reports will be handled with the utmost confidentiality and in accordance with legal requirements and best practices.
        </p>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Code of Conduct</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          All staff, volunteers, and visitors to the school are expected to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• Treat all children with respect and dignity</li>
          <li>• Maintain appropriate boundaries in all interactions</li>
          <li>• Report any concerns about child safety immediately</li>
          <li>• Follow all school policies and procedures</li>
          <li>• Never use physical punishment or emotional abuse</li>
          <li>• Ensure children are supervised appropriately at all times</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Privacy Policy -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-cream">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="heading-primary mb-8">Privacy Policy</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">
          Greencrest Advent School is committed to protecting the privacy and personal information of our students, parents, and website visitors.
        </p>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          We collect information that is necessary for:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• Processing admissions applications</li>
          <li>• Maintaining student records and academic progress</li>
          <li>• Communicating with parents and guardians</li>
          <li>• Ensuring student safety and welfare</li>
          <li>• Complying with legal and regulatory requirements</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Information</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Personal information is used solely for:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• Educational and administrative purposes</li>
          <li>• Communication with families</li>
          <li>• Student safety and welfare</li>
          <li>• Compliance with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We do not sell, rent, or share personal information with third parties except as required by law or with explicit consent.
        </p>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Data Security</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction. This includes secure storage systems, access controls, and regular security reviews.
        </p>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Your Rights</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          Parents and guardians have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• Access their child's personal information</li>
          <li>• Request corrections to inaccurate information</li>
          <li>• Request deletion of information (subject to legal requirements)</li>
          <li>• Withdraw consent for certain uses of information</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Website Privacy</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          When you visit our website:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li>• We may collect basic information such as IP address and browser type</li>
          <li>• We use cookies to improve website functionality (you can disable cookies in your browser)</li>
          <li>• Contact forms collect information you voluntarily provide</li>
          <li>• We do not track users across other websites</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          For questions about our privacy practices or to exercise your rights, please contact:
        </p>
        <div class="bg-green-light/20 p-6 rounded-lg mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Data Protection Officer:</strong><br>
            Email: privacy@greencrestadvent.ac.ke<br>
            Phone: +254 727 568 790<br>
            Address: Greencrest Advent School, 903 Moi's Bridge, Kenya
          </p>
        </div>

        <h3 class="heading-secondary mt-8 mb-4">Policy Updates</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          This privacy policy may be updated from time to time. We will notify parents and guardians of any significant changes. The latest version will always be available on this page.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm italic">
          Last updated: January 2024
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact for Concerns -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-green-dark text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Have Concerns?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-green-light">
        If you have any questions or concerns about safeguarding or privacy, please don't hesitate to contact us.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary bg-white text-green-dark hover:bg-green-light inline-block">
        Contact Us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
